HEADWORD: Tesselar
<hw>Tes"sel*ar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tessella</ets> a small square piece, a little cube, dim. of
<ets>tessera</ets> a square piece of stone, wood, etc., a die.]</ety>
